headline: Big Profit Stocks on Sale: 3 Picks at Yearly Lows.
summary: There were 119 stocks and other investments hitting new 52-week lows on Tuesday. Five of them generate healthy profits but face temporary headwinds that are expected to subside in the future, making them attractive value plays for risk-tolerant investors.
